  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of two combination chemotherapies in the treatment of patients with SLCL

      The combination chemotherapies for this study are Carboplatin plus Irinotecan versus
      Carboplatin plus Etoposide.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
